data.description: Come take a look at this home in Lost Creek that is situated on a larger corner lot. The curb appeal of the front yard is awesome with a big tree and flower beds. The private backyard has a covered patio for your entertaining needs and BBQ's.   This home has most of it's living on the 1st floor. 3 bedrooms, an office, laundry room and 2 baths. Upstairs there is a huge loft that could be turned  into anything you like. It also has 1 bathroom attached.  You will enjoy cooking in your well equipped spacious kitchen with granite counter tops and backsplash which overlooks the roomy living area.  Make an appointment to see this charming home.
